data.name: richTextBox1.Text
data.value:
Load Use to load a dirty map from any directory on your computer (only works for .png files). If successfully loaded, SharpClean will display the image.
Clean Only available after loading a dirty map, This process will remove unwanted dust and clutter determined to not be actually present in the store. A progress bar is provided at the bottom left corner.
Save Only available after cleaning a dirty map. Use to save the cleaned store map. *Do not edit the pregenerated store name
Open Map In Gimp Only available after cleaning a dirty map and saving the file. This will open the original and cleaned images in GIMP for post editing.
Enable Eagle Eye Available after loading a usable map. Displays images of the store taken during mapping.
Additional help can be found by clicking the link below.
